definition: to eject/to exit from/to pop up
to pluck (a string)/to play (a string instrument)/to spring or leap/to shoot (e.g. with a catapult)/(of cotton) to fluff or tease/to flick/to flip/to accuse/to impeach/elastic (of materials)

to go out/to come out/to occur/to produce/to go beyond/to rise/to put forth/to happen/(used after a verb to indicate an outward direction or a positive result)/classifier for dramas, plays, operas etc
variant of 出[chu1] (classifier for plays or chapters of classical novels)

sentences.english: How can they control what pops up on the Internet?
sentences.chinese: 他们能否控制互联网上的弹出消息？

sentences.english: Hitting "4" will pop up a sub-window allowing me to select a view.
sentences.chinese: 按一下“4”将弹出一个选择视图的子窗口。

sentences.english: Enable the item specified by id in the popup menu.
sentences.chinese: 开启弹出式选单中指定代码的项目。

sentences.english: When you select a station, the map zooms in, and ashort message pops up.
sentences.chinese: 当你选到一个站点，地图被放大，一条短消息被弹出。

sentences.english: You should see Operation completed successfully in a pop-up dialog:.
sentences.chinese: 您将在弹出对话框中看到操作成功完成。

sentences.english: Can You Pop an Abscessed Tooth?
sentences.chinese: 你能弹出一个牙床脓肿？。

sentences.english: If you find the popup distracting, you can move the slider to Never.
sentences.chinese: 如果你发现弹出框影响了你，你可以让其消失不再见。

sentences.english: Don't let blinking icons and pop-ups disrupt your work flow.
sentences.chinese: 不要让闪烁的图标和弹出的窗口打断你的工作流程。

sentences.english: Once you believe, then it’s on and popping like popcorn.
sentences.chinese: 一旦你相信，它就会像爆米花一样“砰”地弹出来。

sentences.english: Toggles popup information window for the pointed entry in the playlist.
sentences.chinese: 切换播放列表中鼠标指向的项的弹出信息窗口。

sentences.english: Please make sure you turn off your pop-up blocker.
sentences.chinese: 请确保您关闭您的弹出窗口拦截器。

sentences.english: These cute little Tic Tacs of color are popping up all over the design world.
sentences.chinese: 这些色彩和弹出的可爱小把戏遍布了整个设计界。

sentences.english: You can post new messages from pop-up page after clicking the button.
sentences.chinese: 点击按钮后，你可以在弹出视窗直接发送新的讯息。

sentences.english: Turn off any pop-up blockers you may have on your PC.
sentences.chinese: 关闭你的个人电脑上有关窗口弹出的限制。

sentences.english: You are a Qingcui string, string that pops up on the melody is love.
sentences.chinese: 您是一根轻脆的琴弦，弦上弹出的旋律是爱。

sentences.english: Click on the window and it comes up, ready for use.
sentences.chinese: 点击窗口，窗口就会弹出来，等待使用。
